Pak Nigaki!

276
00:16:04,987 --> 00:16:07,887
Gawat. Dia sudah tidak bernapas.

277
00:16:07,887 --> 00:16:09,387
Dia dipukul sampai mati.

278
00:16:11,187 --> 00:16:12,787
Apa itu?

279
00:16:15,487 --> 00:16:18,987
Cokelat?

280
00:16:19,987 --> 00:16:23,887
Yoshitaka, jawablah!

