00:16:23,887 --> 00:16:27,387
Gawat. Badainya semakin kencang!

282
00:16:27,387 --> 00:16:29,387
Hei, apa yang akan kau lakukan?

283
00:16:29,387 --> 00:16:32,487
Kalau terus mencarinya di tengah gunung begini,

284
00:16:32,487 --> 00:16:34,987
